  - {fileID: 7701993303569800306, guid: 369473aeffddde943b389a711b5b8d78, type: 3}
  recruitLoreLines:
  - "Beyond a cracked archway, Graham finds Sally, a mage flung between fragments
    by the same Sundering that scattered his world. She recognizes the shard in his
    hand \u2014 and the hope it represents. She joins him."
  - In the ruins of a fallen watchtower, Violet the Hunter has been stalking the
    same Portals as Graham, hunting the truth of what tore the sky apart. She sees
    an ally, not a stranger, and falls into step beside him.
  - James, a mercenary stranded when his last contract's world came apart, has given
    up finding his own way home. He offers his blade for passage through Graham's
    Gates instead.
